reviewText: What a roll down memory lane. This is a great video to remember those great bulls players and great games. Video is well done. Shipped quick.. Thanks!

Seller shipping was great, product was in great shape.

The actual program was fun to watch-- too bad it didn't have the Bulls intro, but I guess you can't have everything.  Worth watching.

Watched it the moment I received it.  Excellent from A to Z.
Frank from Montreal
